<view class="page">
  <view wx:if="{{showBackTop}}" class="fab-top" bindtap="onBackTop" hover-class="fab-top-hover">↑</view>
  <view class="tab-bar-sticky">
  <view class="tabs">
    <view
      class="tab {{channel === 'arxiv' ? 'tab-on' : ''}}"
      data-ch="arxiv"
      bindtap="onChannel"
    >arXiv</view>
    <view
      class="tab {{channel === 'journal' ? 'tab-on' : ''}}"
      data-ch="journal"
      bindtap="onChannel"
    >期刊</view>
    <view
      class="tab {{channel === 'conference' ? 'tab-on' : ''}}"
      data-ch="conference"
      bindtap="onChannel"
    >会议</view>
  </view>

  <view class="tabs tabs-sort">
    <view
      class="tab {{sort === 'recommended' ? 'tab-on' : ''}}"
      data-sort="recommended"
      bindtap="onSort"
    >综合</view>
    <view
      class="tab {{sort === 'hot' ? 'tab-on' : ''}}"
      data-sort="hot"
      bindtap="onSort"
    >热门</view>
  </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{loading && items.length === 0}}" class="center">
    <text>加载中…</text>
  </view>
  <view wx:elif="{{error && items.length === 0}}" class="center">
    <text>{{error}}</text>
  </view>
  <view wx:elif="{{!loading && items.length === 0}}" class="empty">
    <block wx:if="{{!blurbsLlmReady}}">
      <text class="empty-title">请先配置大模型</text>
      <text class="empty-desc">推荐只展示已生成「中文摘要（2～3 句）」的论文。请在「设置」填写接口地址、API Key 与模型并保存同步到服务器，然后下拉刷新。</text>
    </block>
    <block wx:else>
      <text class="empty-title">暂无条目</text>
      <text class="empty-desc">当前频道下还没有带中文摘要的论文，或摘要仍在生成中。请稍后下拉刷新；也可在「订阅配置」调整关键词、期刊与会议后再下拉抓取。</text>
      <text wx:if="{{channel === 'conference'}}" class="empty-hint">会议频道依赖 OpenAlex 会议数据；可在订阅中添加会议 Source ID。</text>
    </block>
  </view>

  <view wx:else class="list-wrap">
    <paper-card
      wx:for="{{items}}"
      wx:key="id"
      paper="{{item}}"
      position="{{index}}"
      bind:open="onOpenPaper"
    />
    <button
      wx:if="{{nextCursor}}"
      class="more-btn"
      loading="{{loadingMore}}"
      bindtap="loadMore"
    >加载更多</button>
  </view>
</view>
